data.description:
Nestled amidst the enchanting woodlands of Woodridge Lake Estates, this luxurious cedar mountain home is the perfect sanctuary for those seeking serenity and modern amenities. Spanning  generous 2,999 sq. ft., this captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bath, 3.22 acre estate offers a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of city life. A sophisticated blend of style and comfort. As you step inside this beautifully designed cedar home, you'll instantly notice the exquisite attention to detail with quality craftsmanship at every turn. The airy, open floor plan effortlessly flows from the inviting living area to the stylish, well-appointed kitchen. The master bedroom boasts an expansive walk-in closet, a cozy window seat, a relaxing jetted tub, and a separate shower for an indulging personal retreat. Unrivaled amenities and thoughtful touches *
Designed with functionality in mind, the home features two additional bedrooms, including a unique, spacious loft outfitted with two double-sized Murphy beds. The estate also offers a versatile office/laundry area, ample storage throughout, and a dedicated, fully-equipped wine cellar to delight the most discerning connoisseurs. You'll never have to worry about power outages with the reliable central heating system and the dependable backup generator.
Breathtaking natural surroundings *
Situated on an enviable lot in desirable Woodridge Lake Estates, this mountain residence allows you to enjoy the wonders of nature at your doorstep - without sacrificing any modern conveniences. The detached two-car garage also includes a convenient storage shed.
Don't Miss Out on This Sublime Mountain Hideaway
This elegant cedar mountain home is the epitome of luxury living, offering a harmonious blend of modern amenities, unparalleled craftsmanship, and picturesque surroundings. Don't let your dream retreat slip away - act now and experience the exquisite serenity that awaits you in Shingletown, California. Woodridge Lake privileges include lake access.
Go to woodridgepoa.org for more information about the subdivision.
